# Python Project 5 (Midterm)

# Project 1

- This program allows the user to enter the number of books purchased in a month and calculates the reward points earned based on a fixed points system.
- It uses a simple Tkinter interface with input validation and displays the result directly on the screen.

# Project 2.1

- This program reads data from a CSV file and allows the user to view calendar dates, building names, or faculty names by clicking buttons.
- The results are displayed inside a Tkinter window along with a CCSU logo.

# Project 2.2

- This is an extended version of the previous data viewer that includes additional buttons for School of Business and MIS Department data.
-  It improves layout, formatting, and error handling while displaying filtered CSV data inside a professional-looking Tkinter interface.
